public class PushButtonREditor
extends AbstractTableCellEditor
implements javax.swing.table.TableCellRenderer

This class is a table cell renderer and editor. It presents a push button. You should attach an actionListener to this class. Use event.getSource().getClientProperty("TABLEROW"); to get the row number as an Integer.
